OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fstart to the night with high cloud
OL,7,Faround. Low cloud and a few showers
OL,8,Farrive in the west in the early hours,
OL,9,Fbut a much more comfortable night for
OL,10,Fmany.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FLow cloud to start with, but
OL,13,Flifting through the morning and into
OL,14,Fthe afternoon. Isolated showers
OL,15,Fdeveloping, with sunny spells in
OL,16,Fbetween. Warm, but cooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
